\c 2
\s Esiteri anoitwa vahosi panzvimbo yaVhashiti
\p
\v 1 Zvino shure kwaizvozvo, kutsamwa kwamambo Ahashivheroshi kwakati kwanyarara, akarangarira Vhashiti nezvaakaita, nechirevo chakatemwa pamusoro pake.
\v 2 Ipapo varanda vamambo vaimubatira, vakati: Mambo ngaatsvakirwe mhandara dzakanaka;
\v 3 mambo ngaaise vatariri pamativi ese oushe hwake, vaunganidze mhandara dzese dzakanaka paShushani nhare yamambo, paimba yavakadzi, vachengetwe naHegai muranda wamambo, mutariri wavakadzi; vapiwewo zvavangazvinatsa nazvo.
\v 4 Zvino musikana unofarirwa namambo ngaave vahosi panzvimbo yaVhashiti. Izvozvo zvikafadza mambo, akaita saizvozvo.
\p
\v 5 Zvino paShushani panhare yamambo pakange panomuJudha, ainzi Modhekai, mwanakomana waJairi, mwanakomana waShimei, mwanakomana waKishi, muBhenjamini,
\v 6 akange atapwa Jerusarema, pamwe chete navatapwa vakange vatapwa naJekonia mambo waJudha, wakange atapwa naNebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi.
\v 7 Iye akange arera Hadhasha, ndiye Esiteri, mukunda wababamunini wake; nokuti akange asina baba namai; zvino musikana uyu akange akanaka paumiro hwake napachiso chake; pakufa kwababa vake namai vake Modhekai ndokumutora, akamuita mukunda wake.
\p
\v 8 Zvino murairo wamambo nechirevo chake zvakati zvanzwikwa, vasikana vazhinji vakaunganidzwa paShushani nhare yamambo, pavaichengetwa naHegai, Esiteri akatorwawo, akaiswa mumba mamambo, akachengetwa naHegai mutariri wavakadzi.
\v 9 Musikana uyu akamufadza, akanzwirwa tsitsi naye, akachimbidzika kumupa zvaangazvinatsa nazvo, nemigove yake yezvokudya uye vasikana vanomwe vaakafanira kupiwa, vaibva paimba yamambo; akamuisa iye navasikana vake pakange pakaisvonaka paimba yavakadzi.
\v 10 Asi Esiteri akange asina kuvazivisa rudzi rwake nehama dzake, nokuti Modhekai akange amuraira, kuti arege kuvazivisa izvozvo.
\v 11 Zvino Modhekai aifamba pamberi pochivanze cheimba yavakadzi mazuva ese, agoziva kuti Esiteri akadini, uye kuti vachaitei naye.
\p
\v 12 Zvino dzoro romusikana umwe neumwe rakati richisvika kupinda kuna mambo Ahashivheroshi, kana aitirwa zvese nomurairo wavakadzi mwedzi ine gumi nemiviri (nokuti mazuva okuchenurwa kwavo akapera kudai, mwedzi mitanhatu vachizora mafuta emura, mwedzi mitanhatu zvinonhuhwira, uye zvimwe zvinhu zvokunatsa vakadzi nazvo),
\v 13 zvino musikana akapinda nomutoo akadaro kuna mambo, uye chinhu chipi nechipi chaaida aichipiwa, kuti abude nacho paimba yavakadzi, apinde mumba mamambo.
\v 14 Aienda madekwani, ndokudzokera mangwana kuimba yechipiri yavakadzi, paaichengetwa naShaashigazi, muranda wamambo, aichengeta varongo; haazaipindazve kuna mambo, asi kana achinge afarirwa namambo, akadanwa nezita rake.
\p
\v 15 Zvino dzoro raEsiteri mukunda waAbhihairi, babamunini vaModhekai, akange amutora akamuita mukunda wake, rakati richisvika rokupinda kuna mambo, haana kukumbira chinhu asi izvochetezvakange zvarairwa naHegai muranda wamambo, mutariri wavakadzi. Zvino Esiteri akanzwirwa tsitsi navese vaimuona.
\v 16 Naizvozvo Esiteri akaiswa kuna mambo Ahashivheroshi mumba yake youshe nomwedzi wegumi, ndiwo mwedzi weTebheti, pagore rechinomwe rokubata kwake ushe.
\v 17 Mambo akada Esiteri kupfuura vamwe vakadzi vese, akanzwira tsitsi nounyoro naye kupfuura dzimwe mhandara dzese; naizvozvo akaisa korona youhosi pamusoro wake, akamuita vahosi panzvimbo yaVhashiti.
\v 18 Ipapo mambo akaitira machinda ake ese navaranda vake vese mutambo mukuru, uri mutambo waEsiteri; akaraira zororo pamativi enyika, akagovera zvipo, mambo asinganyimi napadiki.
\v 19 Zvino pakuunganidzwa kwemhandara rwechipiri, Modhekai akange agere pasuwo ramambo.
\v 20 Esiteri akange achigere kuvazivisa hama dzake kana rudzi rwake, sezvaakarairwa naModhekai; nokuti Esiteri akateerera murairo waModhekai, sezvaaisiita acharerwa naye.
\p
\v 21 Zvino pamazuva iwayo Modhikai agere pasuwo ramambo, varanda vaviri vamambo, Bhigitani naTereshi, pakati pavarindi vomukova, vakatsamwa vakatsvaka kuuraya mambo Ahashivheroshi.
\v 22 Chinhu icho chikazikanwa naModhekai, iye ndokuzivisa vahosi Esiteri, Esiteri akanoudza mambo nezita raModhekai.
\v 23 Zvino vakati vachinzvera chinhu icho, vakawana kuti zvirokwazvo, vese vari vaviri vakasungirirwa pamuti; zvikanyorwa mubhuku yaMakoronike pamberi pamambo.
